@{par}These images are just a bunch which @{"myself and Leo Davidson" LINK "Author"} made (mostly a
cut & paste operation from the @{"many archives" LINK "Thanks"} of beatifully drawn @{"MWB" LINK "MWB"} icons
which exist on Aminet), however, some are hand-drawn and all in all this
archive still took quite a bit of time to compile.
@{par}
@{par}@{b}NOTE:@{ub} The @{fg fill}ToolBarArrow.image@{fg text} is a replacement for the cycle gadget in the
@{par}      lister_toolbarmenu (the name must remain @{b}as is@{ub} in order to work).

