@{par}   patch :) and included seperate guide for it in the @{"c drawer" LINK "C"}.
@{par} · Fixed up the CLI and DOpus drawer icons and added an icon for @{"PaletteShove" LINK "PS"}.
@{par} · Added an @{"ARexx drawer" LINK "ARexx"} with two scripts written by @{"Leo Davidson" LINK "Author"}.
@{par}
@{par}@{fg fill}Release 5:@{fg text}
